Program: Outlook
Title: My Dad, Muhammad Ali
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3cswt6g
Last Broadcast Date: Sat 13 Oct 2018
What is it like to be the daughter of a sporting legend? To many, Muhammad Ali was known as The Greatest, whether as a boxing hero, a pioneering civil rights campaigner, or a world-class entertainer. To Hana Ali though, he was the man who put on magic shows for strangers and recorded interviews with her crushes at school. Image: a young Hana Ali and her father Muhammad Ali Credit: Hana Ali Presenter: Emily Webb Show less